\dfrac{2}{y_{n+1}} = \dfrac{1}{x_n} + \dfrac{1}{y_n}
\frac{x_{n+1}}{x_n}=\frac{1}{2}\left(1+\frac{y_n}{x_n}\right)
\frac{y_n}{y_{n+1}} =\frac{1}{2}\left(1+\frac{y_n}{x_n}\right)
