x_n = \frac{x_{n-1}+y_{n-1}}{2} \leq \frac{ x_{n-1}+x_{n-1}}{2}=x_{n-1}
y_n=\frac{2}{\frac{1}{x_{n-1}}+\frac{1}{y_{n-1}}}\geq\frac{2}{\frac{1}{y_{n-1}}+\frac{1}{y_{n-1}}}=y_{n-1}
